import uiPreview from "./uiPreview"

import header from "./header/uiSchema"
import media from "./media/uiSchema"
import details from "./details/uiSchema"

export default {
    "ui:preview": uiPreview,
    "ui:field": "pageEditor",
    "ui:fieldset": [
        "content"
    ],
    "content": {
        "ui:layout": "pageContent",
        "ui:fieldset": [
            "header",
            "details",
            "media"
        ],
        "header": header,
        "details": details,
        "media": media
    }
}
